v1.0.2 — Comprehensive code review fixes

- customize.sh: ps -A fallback (ps -e) for minimal shells; getprop || true guards
- service.sh: retry loop (5 attempts) instead of fixed sleep
- property_hook.cpp: st_name bounds check (heuristic > 1MB); logcat logging via __android_log_print
- main.cpp: check apply_property_hooks return; removed dead g_env; logcat logging
- config.cpp: list() now returns copy (was dangling reference under lock)
- ghostboot.hpp: list() signature changed to return by value
- MainActivity.kt: exact package match for banking detection; system package blacklist
- GhostBootService.kt: dedup syncTargets (skip write if unchanged); removed dead SOCKET_PATH
- module.prop: version bump to v1.0.2
